"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Some people oppose talking about ideals, future, and realm. They think that such bosses are hypocritical and not pragmatic. Aren't we all together to make money?\\n\\nWhen I first started my business, I told my partners in the same way that we must be realistic, just to make money, don’t talk about ideals, realms, and the future. Even so, our business will soon be on the right track and we will also make money. I got the money, but I found that everyone didn't respect me very much, no big or small with me, and always broke my rules. Then I thought about it. Realized a truth.\\n\\nIn front of the core team, we have to talk about our ideals, our future, and our realm. People are actually similar to light bulbs. When they are not powered on, take a closer look. They are covered with dust, and there may be flies and shit, which is useless. But when the electricity is turned on, it shines brightly and illuminates others.\\n\\nPeople talk about their ideals, their future, and their realm. In fact, they are like light bulbs when they are energized. They begin to shine and illuminate others.\\n\\nEveryone knows that Jack Ma is not good-looking. If he doesn't talk about ideals, future, hope, realm, dreams, and value all day long. Don't say that women like him, even if men think that very few people like him. But he just relied on his ideals, the future, and the realm to illuminate many people, make himself shine, and even become the god in many people's minds, giving others direction in life.\\n\\nIf you don’t talk about this, no one will bother you even if your personal relationship with the core team is good.\\n\\n108 Entrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs\\n\\nIf you look at you from the bottom, if you can't establish a good image, people will have little influence. Thinking about this issue further, I found that religions and parties rely on their ideals, future, and realm to establish their own leadership image and build their own influence.\\n\\nSo my conclusion is that bosses and leaders all eat imagery. Comrade Ma Yun is a typical example. Then, bosses, it is necessary to talk about ideals, the future, and the realm.\",\"timestamp\":1634795976,\"title\":\"Why does the boss talk about ideals, future, and realm?\"},\"digest\":\"yEJAk6ybS6dhXlIJUra6r37CT1vL6vZ-4q9hxK0qn5c\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0500e3b6f7b1214a11851b9B348020C08018403b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"zhRPPi2UPmgg6XARi06A-cK_Y4_nT5XrjJkRIjHZjiuDiW1b3gTKtxubxvT8c_5E7fxL30zKZInFgKGEDrAqlA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1c6f856baad7dbcdc04a289cfb8c27fd2d4c254469eae7a6d5e283ce19250e091ab85676074d27b49e23c7d4b78b5f81e8536a0da448b30920c0f4dc5a6602e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"yEJAk6ybS6dhXlIJUra6r37CT1vL6vZ-4q9hxK0qn5c\"}"